parameters.name: Bx
parameters.description: Spacecraft coordinates x-component of the magetic field.

parameters.name: By
parameters.description: Spacecraft coordinates y-component of the magetic field.

parameters.name: Bz
parameters.description: Spacecraft coordinates z-component of the magetic field.

parameters.name: Bmag
parameters.description: Magnitude (sqrt of sum of squares) of the field component averages.

parameters.name: RMS Bx
parameters.description: Root-mean-square deviation of Bx over the averaging interval.

parameters.name: RMS By
parameters.description: Root-mean-square deviation of By over the averaging interval.

parameters.name: RMS Bz
parameters.description: Root-mean-square deviation of Bz over the averaging interval.

parameters.name: NPTS
parameters.description: Number of points in the average.
